The paper also discusses the use of differential privacy, which is a common technique in cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper involves the use of algorithms and data structures to handle the incremental nature of the data, which is a topic in data structures (cs.DS). The paper also involves the use of optimization techniques, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
